metadata.name: Looking to the future
metadata.description:
The golden Katana holds infinite possibilities. While sharpening its Katana, Spirit is looking straight into the future and listening for opportunities.


This is an illustration of Azuki#5558 Spirit, which won 15th place in a contest sponsored by Aeralytx. This illustration was a challenge for me and a very special one.
Thank you Aeralytx!


2000px ✕ 2000px・350dpi
